episodes.title: #3226 RHOBH S15E10: Cult Following
episodes.description: The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills explores Amanda’s journey into and out of a Florida cult while the Hamptons crew parties in Montauk. Then, Denise returns to the show for a sobering scene with Erika and Sutton.
